</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>成人女優利用元宇宙攪 Party   元宇宙 JAV 樂園將於 Sandbox 成立</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/25/javpark/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=javpark</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Dec 2021 06:39:33 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078256</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>日本性感女優橋本有菜（橋本ありな）宣佈將會於元宇宙 The Sandbox 搞派對，成為第一個在元宇宙搞派對的 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>日本性感女優橋本有菜（橋本ありな）宣佈將會於元宇宙 The Sandbox 搞派對，成為第一個在元宇宙搞派對的性感女優。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">Merry Christmas🎄<br />仮想空間メタバースでパーティを開く初めての女優になることができてとてもうれしいです！<br />So excited to be the 1st actress to host a party in Metaverse!</p><p>Arina Day 2022 <a href="https://twitter.com/avycnft?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@avycnft</a><br />遊びに来てね💕<br />事前登録受付中:<a href="https://t.co/yNAQyTA9sS">https://t.co/yNAQyTA9sS</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Metaverse?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Metaverse</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/NFT?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#NFT</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/TheSandboxGame?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@TheSandboxGame</a> <a href="https://t.co/oxsaj2rm3h">pic.twitter.com/oxsaj2rm3h</a></p><p>&mdash; 橋本ありな (@Arinahashimoto1) <a href="https://twitter.com/Arinahashimoto1/status/1474255280024473609?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 24, 2021</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在昨日聖誕除夕（24 日）橋本有菜於個人 Twitter 宣佈將會在元宇宙空間 The Sandbox 搞派對。The Sandbox 將會建立「AV Wonderland」召集成人電影愛好者。在派對開始之前她已透露了個人在 The Sandbox 的肖像。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.59.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078258" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.59-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.59-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.59-768x514.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.59.jpg 834w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在背後搞派對的 AVYC，已在 The Sandbox 購入了 2 塊 3&#215;3 的土地，將會興建 JAV 主題樂園，當中會有魔法鏡子車以及成人影片中經常出現的著名情節。AVYC 現在已成為一個有 10000 NFT 的集合，收集了各種區塊鏈上的收藏品，而主題樂園將可使用專用貨幣 $AVGL 入場與交易 。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078257" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-694x475.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="475" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-694x475.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-1280x877.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-768x526.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-1536x1052.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-2048x1403.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/Arinahashimoto1/status/1474255280024473609">Twitter</a>, <a href="https://avyc.io/?code=TkSrJJJ">AVYC</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
