</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>日本教授發明「可舔式」有味道電視，烹飪節目食物可供觀眾「品嚐」</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/25/tastetv/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=tastetv</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Dec 2021 04:16:00 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078147</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>日本明治大學教授宮下芳明開發出一款「可舔式」電視，在視覺以外為用戶提供味覺體驗。 &#160; 這款電視叫品嚐 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>日本明治大學教授宮下芳明開發出一款「可舔式」電視，在視覺以外為用戶提供味覺體驗。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078154" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25-694x424.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="424" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25-694x424.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25-768x469.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25.jpg 1201w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.51.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078149" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.51-694x369.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.51-694x369.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.51-768x409.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.51.jpg 1261w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078152" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29-768x329.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29.jpg 1279w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>這款電視叫品嚐電視「Taste the TV」，簡稱為「TTTV」。電視裡面內置一個薄膜以及含有不同味道的液體，電視會根據要求，從 10 款甜酸苦辣為基礙味道的液體中，選出合適的味道並按比例噴灑到畫面上，模擬出食物味道。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.00.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078150" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.00.jpg" alt="" width="510" height="553" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.41.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078148" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.41-694x377.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.41-694x377.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.41-768x417.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.41.jpg 1042w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.33.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078155" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.33-694x376.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.33-694x376.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.33-768x416.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.33.jpg 1181w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>當電視在熒幕顯示食物時，用戶可用舌頭舔嚐到味道，同時滿足視覺與聽覺體驗。教授指目前電視可模擬出 20 款不同食物的味道。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078153" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50-768x496.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50.jpg 1210w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.00.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.18.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078151" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.18-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.18-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.18-768x439.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.18.jpg 1193w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>宮下芳明教授指電視可用作調酒師、廚師的教學影片，也可用來品嚐食物或玩猜謎遊戲。他更希望可開發一個像音樂串流平台的系統，讓用家可「下載」世界各地不同味道。</p><p>商用版 TTTV 的成本為每部 10 萬日元（約港幣 7000 元）。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_66478"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rt0CsOAls-s?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：YouTube</p></p><div class="feedflare">
