</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Google Drive 將審查用戶文件，禁止分享仇恨言論、恐怖主義相關檔案</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/25/updates-this-official-feed-from-the-google-workspace-team-provides-essential-information-about-new-features-and-improvements-for-google-workspace-customers/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=updates-this-official-feed-from-the-google-workspace-team-provides-essential-information-about-new-features-and-improvements-for-google-workspace-customers</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Dec 2021 04:12:10 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google blog]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google Drive]]></category><category><![CDATA[審查]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1077346</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Google 近日公佈了針對「Google Drive」雲端硬碟服務的新版「使用政策」，表明 Google 將 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Google 近日公佈了針對「Google Drive」雲端硬碟服務的新版「使用政策」，表明 Google 將有權審查用戶存放於雲端硬碟的內容，若內容違反政策，用戶將收到官方發送的 Email 警告；在該違規的檔案名稱上，也會標註禁止公開分享。新政策將先向 Google Workspace、G Suite Basic 和 Business 企業版的用戶推行。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1077347" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/046E3F42-1C05-485E-B002-5DEB8E91D660.png" alt="" width="640" height="341" /></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1077348" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/969D0DA9-E4E0-400B-8B1A-C81DFF0AA11A-694x438.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/969D0DA9-E4E0-400B-8B1A-C81DFF0AA11A-694x438.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/969D0DA9-E4E0-400B-8B1A-C81DFF0AA11A-1280x809.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/969D0DA9-E4E0-400B-8B1A-C81DFF0AA11A-768x485.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/969D0DA9-E4E0-400B-8B1A-C81DFF0AA11A-1536x970.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/969D0DA9-E4E0-400B-8B1A-C81DFF0AA11A-2048x1294.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/969D0DA9-E4E0-400B-8B1A-C81DFF0AA11A.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">對於共享雲端硬碟中的文件，共享雲端硬盤管理員會收到通知，這將有助於確保 Google Drive 項目的所有者完全瞭解其內容的狀態，同時有助於確保用戶免受濫用內容的侵害。不論其中包含詳細資訊，以及他們可以採取哪些措施來請求審核。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據官網顯示，若檔案涉及如垃圾訊息、惡意軟件及詐騙、仇恨言論、恐怖主義相關內容、騷擾、罷凌和威脅、色情內容、兒童剝削相關內容、假冒他人、私人和機密資訊、非法活動、公開串流播放內容、侵權以及使用與提交內容，用戶帳號、檔案都有可能會被強制移除。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Google 表示，希望新政策可令用戶瞭解違規情況，同時告知他們可採取什麼措施以請求重新審核；另外也是為避免有人濫用文件網址連結的散播功能，以保其他使用者不會受到惡意行為的侵害。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://workspaceupdates.googleblog.com/2021/12/abuse-notification-emails-google-drive.html">Google Blog</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=NQEo3zx_OJ8:oK0oR9fQ6sw:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=NQEo3zx_OJ8:oK0oR9fQ6sw:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>全球首個 Tesla baby 順利出世，靠自動駕駛穩住電動車</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/25/philadelphia-woman-gives-birth-in-front-seat-of-tesla-on-autopilot/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=philadelphia-woman-gives-birth-in-front-seat-of-tesla-on-autopilot</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Dec 2021 04:09:40 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Tesla]]></category><category><![CDATA[自動駕駛]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1077325</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Tesla 曾多次表示，駕駛者目前不可完全依賴自動駕駛系統，依然需要坐在駕駛席並手握軚盤，令不少人質疑其自動駕 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Tesla 曾多次表示，駕駛者目前不可完全依賴自動駕駛系統，依然需要坐在駕駛席並手握軚盤，令不少人質疑其自動駕駛系統形同雞肋。但早前就有一宗「 Tesla 意外事件」令人十分窩心，在 Tesla 自動駕駛的輔助下，美國一名孕婦平安在車內誕下女兒，成為全球首個 Tesla Baby。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1077326" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/91BCC5AF-28E9-417D-9E63-D5D4211FFC17-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/91BCC5AF-28E9-417D-9E63-D5D4211FFC17-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/91BCC5AF-28E9-417D-9E63-D5D4211FFC17.jpeg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今年 9 月，美國費城一名孕婦 Yiran 和她的丈夫，帶同三歲的兒子在趕往醫院途中，由於交通擠塞被困。看著妻子陣痛越趨嚴重，丈夫無奈下將 Tesla 設定為 Autopilot (自動駕駛) 讓電腦控制車輛，以便照顧太太及安撫兒子的情緒，最終讓 Yiran 在車內順利誕下一位女嬰。在她們到達醫院前，寶寶已經在車上出世，等候的醫護人員在打開車門之後，便立即替寶寶剪斷臍帶，確認嬰兒的健康狀況。經過這次事件，Yiran 考慮為女兒命名為 Tess，紀念這刺激的生產過程。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1077327" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CD4036AD-0BDF-4D1B-92C5-4242634A6D6D-674x580.jpeg" alt="" width="674" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CD4036AD-0BDF-4D1B-92C5-4242634A6D6D-674x580.jpeg 674w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CD4036AD-0BDF-4D1B-92C5-4242634A6D6D-1046x900.jpeg 1046w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CD4036AD-0BDF-4D1B-92C5-4242634A6D6D-768x661.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CD4036AD-0BDF-4D1B-92C5-4242634A6D6D.jpeg 1261w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 674px" /></span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">My wife courageously delivered our baby girl, Maeve, in the front seat of our ⁦<a href="https://twitter.com/Tesla?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Tesla</a>⁩ model 3 en route to the hospital &#8211; here’s the story ⁦<a href="https://twitter.com/PhillyInquirer?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@PhillyInquirer</a>⁩ ! ⁦⁦<a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@elonmusk</a>⁩ ⁦<a href="https://twitter.com/Tesla?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Tesla</a> thx for the autopilot⁩ 🤝💯 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/tesbaby?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#tesbaby</a>  <a href="https://t.co/JPMfh7AyhN">https://t.co/JPMfh7AyhN</a></p><p>&mdash; Keating Sherry (@KeatingSherry) <a href="https://twitter.com/KeatingSherry/status/1471315682570772482?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 16, 2021</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">有評論表示，現時各大車廠研究的自動駕駛系統已達至 Level 3 等級，理論上的確可以完全透過電腦來駕駛，但由於不同地區路況和民眾駕駛態度存在差異，未必每個地方也會適用。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2021/dec/19/tesla-baby-philadelphia-autopilot">The Guardian</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=j0qJztA-ROQ:9XvZ9KYCmLI:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=j0qJztA-ROQ:9XvZ9KYCmLI:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>攔阻調查人員進入倉庫  Amazon 被指妨礙職安調查</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/25/amazon-bar-officials-from-entering-warhouse/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=amazon-bar-officials-from-entering-warhouse</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[高威]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Dec 2021 04:03:29 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078084</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>據外媒報道，Amazon 過去六個月曾經妨礙有關其在西雅圖南部倉庫的職業安全調查，華盛頓州司法部在法庭上更指  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>據外媒報道，Amazon 過去六個月曾經妨礙有關其在西雅圖南部倉庫的職業安全調查，華盛頓州司法部在法庭上更指 Amazon 曾經攔阻調查人員進入其設施。</p><figure id="attachment_1078093" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1078093" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gettyimages-825338322-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1078093 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gettyimages-825338322-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gettyimages-825338322-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gettyimages-825338322-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gettyimages-825338322-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gettyimages-825338322-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gettyimages-825338322-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/gettyimages-825338322-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1078093" class="wp-caption-text">圖片來源：Scott Olson/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>今年五月，美國司法部曾起訴 Amazon，曾指 Amazon 在西雅圖南部的倉庫違反勞工法例，包括逼使員工在非常匆忙的節奏下工作，又不給予足夠時間讓員工康復，形成危險的工作環境。</p><p>調查又發現，Amazon 的訂單處理中心的工傷人數比起業界標準高出一倍，而在杜邦市（DuPont）的倉庫更是比起其他 Amazon 訂單處理中心的高工傷率。</p><p>調查人員在法庭的文件指，Amazon 曾經多次直接地「阻礙搜集證據」（undermine our data collection）。其中一次 Amazon 阻撓調查人員在休息後，再次進入其設施搜集證據，要求調查人員必須有法庭手令才可進入；另外一次則指，當調查人員正在觀察他們的工作情況時，常常刻意以「必須離開並進入訓練為由」，促使其工人離開工作地點。</p><p>調查人員又指 Amazon 拒絕提供所需調查資料，或者提供不完整的資料。現時西雅圖法院上星期已發出手令，准許調查人員完全進入其倉庫。現時 Amazon 開展了一個「工作安全計劃」（Workplace-safety initiatives）以減低工傷，但調查人員質疑此計劃是否有成效。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/amazon-washington-workplace-safety-regulators-investigation-court-documents-2021-12?utm_source=facebook.com&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=sf-bi-ti&amp;fbclid=IwAR3fp3rW3SKjasL4oQKEMUwcoTy9R8ih3ko_7PCZMnO07TkzMG7-zYl7Qd4">Business Insider</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=usGo5XYkzrw:wpV6-newsec:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=usGo5XYkzrw:wpV6-newsec:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Intel 揚言禁用新疆勞工，中國網民揚言抵制後道歉收場</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/25/intel-yield-at-chinese-citizens/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=intel-yield-at-chinese-citizens</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[高威]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Dec 2021 04:02:46 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078095</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>多間美國生產商，都十分關注新疆的勞工人權問題，早前 Intel 則發出公開信，要求不使用任何來自新疆的勞工、採 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>多間美國生產商，都十分關注新疆的勞工人權問題，早前 Intel 則發出公開信，要求不使用任何來自新疆的勞工、採購產品或服務。但中國官媒及大陸網民、代言明星等即時抵制及終止合作。 Intel 則在微信發出中文聲明，強調對中國深懷敬意，對於尊敬的中國客戶帶來困擾，深表歉意。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.55.51.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.55.51-694x327.png" alt="" width="694" height="327" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.55.51-694x327.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.55.51-1280x604.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.55.51-768x362.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.55.51-1536x724.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.55.51-2048x966.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.55.51.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Intel 在發出公開信後，隨即被中國媒體觀察者網發現。Intel 以在官網以簡體中文、正體中文、英文、日文等多種語言表示「不用任何來自新疆的勞動力、採購商品和服務」。報道出街後，引來《環球時報》社評批評 Intel 此要求「極其荒謬，又十分刺眼」，Intel 於中國的代言人王俊凱 Karry Wang 更表示即日起終止與 Intel 的合作，表明「國家利益高於一切！」</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170807459.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170807459-694x281.png" alt="" width="694" height="281" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170807459-694x281.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170807459-768x311.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170807459.png 1101w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221171811150.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221171811150-694x210.png" alt="" width="694" height="210" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221171811150-694x210.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221171811150-768x233.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221171811150.png 805w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><figure id="attachment_1078178" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1078178" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170710751.png"><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1078178 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170710751-694x305.png" alt="" width="694" height="305" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170710751-694x305.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170710751-1280x562.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170710751-768x337.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170710751-1536x674.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221170710751.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1078178" class="wp-caption-text">Intel 在官網中曾經以多種語言發布聲明。</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1078181" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1078181" style="width: 440px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.58.03.png"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1078181" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.58.03-440x580.png" alt="" width="440" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.58.03-440x580.png 440w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.58.03-683x900.png 683w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.58.03-768x1012.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.58.03-1165x1536.png 1165w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-下午 3.58.03.png 1214w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 440px" /></a><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1078181" class="wp-caption-text">王俊凱工作室發表聲明，指終止與 Intel 一切合作。（來源：微博截圖）</figcaption></figure><p>中國網民對 Intel 此舉亦非常大反應，直言要抵制 Intel。Intel 今日終在微信發出中文聲明，表示發表該公開信的「初衷是確保遵守美國法律」，又表示現在「借此澄清，信中的關於新疆的段落只出於表述合規合法的初衷，並非它意或表達立場。」</p><figure id="attachment_1078183" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1078183" style="width: 437px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221174107491.png"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1078183" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221174107491-437x580.png" alt="" width="437" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221174107491-437x580.png 437w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221174107491-679x900.png 679w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20211221174107491.png 705w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 437px" /></a><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1078183" class="wp-caption-text">網民反應（來源：微博截圖）</figcaption></figure><p>據統計，中國市場為 Intel 的最大盈利來源，2020 年已佔 202.6 億美元，無怪乎 Intel 必須急急澄清。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.guancha.cn/economy/2021_12_21_619362.shtml">觀察者網</a>、<a href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-china-apologises-over-xinjiang-supplier-statement-2021-12-23/">路透社</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=v1TSVEC9TlI:2nGLxTLptIA:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=v1TSVEC9TlI:2nGLxTLptIA:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
